                        <interp inst="t18341205-name-187" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN FRANCIS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a pawnbroker, and live in High-street, Poplar. I have a watch pawned for 14<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., on the 28th, between seven and eight o'clock in the evening, by the prisoner.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">Property produced and sworn to.</hi>)</p>
               <p>The prisoner put in a petition for a lenient sentence, stating himself to have been intoxicated at the time he committed the robbery. The prose<lb></lb>cutor and officers both gave him a good character.)</p>
